ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.v281.group

Class CCR_I16_GOAL

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.AbstractStructure
      • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.AbstractGroup
        • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.v281.group.CCR_I16_GOAL
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Group, Structure, Visitable, Serializable

    public class CCR_I16_GOAL
extends AbstractGroup

    Represents a CCR_I16_GOAL group structure (a Group object). A Group is an ordered collection of message segments that can repeat together or be optionally in/excluded together. This Group contains the following elements:

    • 1: GOL (Goal Detail)
    • 2: VAR (Variance) optional repeating
    • 3: CCR_I16_ROLE_GOAL (a Group object) optional repeating
    • 4: CCR_I16_GOAL_OBSERVATION (a Group object) optional repeating
    See Also:
